dct_title_s: Ringgold County, Iowa, 1947, aerial photomosaic index
dct_description_sm: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol BKQ. Form of individual image numbering: BKQ-1D-[number], BKQ-2D-[number], or BKQ-3D-[number]."Flying completed Sept. 22, 1947." Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, Kentucky. "Approximate scale, 1:20,000" [refers to individual images from which mosaic was made].
